Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Hali Maintainers <maintainers@hali.local>
Depends: systemd
Description: Hali local-first model cache daemon and CLI
 Hali downloads and caches GGUF models locally and optionally seeds
 them on the LAN through a background daemon.
